- Grade {{ grade }}: {{ subjects | join(", ") }}
{% endfor %}

{% if available_topics %}
Available topics for Grade {{ session_grade }} {{ session_subject }}:
{% for t in available_topics %}
- {{ t.name }}
{% endfor %}

IMPORTANT: The "topic" field MUST be one of the topic names listed above, or null if the student's request does not match any topic. Do NOT invent topic names. Pick the closest matching topic from the list.
{% endif %}

Only use grade and subject combinations from the curriculum list. If the student mentions a subject or grade not available, set it to null.

